response.overview: The 2025 WrestleDream was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) event produced by the American promotion All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It was the third WrestleDream event and took place on October 18, 2025, at the Chaifetz Arena in St. Louis, Missouri. Like the previous events, this will be a tribute event in honor of New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) founder Antonio Inoki, who passed away on October 1, 2022.
response.title: AEW: WrestleDream 2025
